            <li><a href="https://bit.ly/2NYeWRD">Stateless Example: PHP Guestbook with Redis</a></li>

        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Reference</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=517851">Glossary</a></li>
